original_title: Official Fresh Prince of Bel-Air Parody
overview: When this West Philly home boy moves to the cloistered California neighborhood of Bel-Air, he barely knows what hit him. But in the adult DVD Official Fresh Prince of Bel Air Parody, he learns fast that to fit in, he better hit everything in town, including Candice Nicole, Misty Stone, and Imani Rose. Trying to get along with his uptight cousin Hilary and his horny cousin Carlton who's always trying to get laid, Will discovers that a man of his 'ability' just might find his place in Bel-Air after all.
title: Official Fresh Prince of Bel-Air Parody
